name: SpaceJump (Dragonmann)
description:
You play as an astronaut about to enter a mysterious portal. Once you jump through you realize, that you are stuck in the tractor beam of a UFO. Can you survive the longest?

Used assets:

  • Low Poly Ultimate Pack | polyperfect
  • GUI PRO Kit - Sci-Fi | Layer Lab
  • Basic Motions | Kevin Iglesias
  • Modular Motion | Neil V.
  • POLYGON Icons Pack - Low Poly 3D Art by Synty | Synty
  • Sci-Fi Arsenal | Archanor VFX
  • AllSky | RPGWHITELOCK
  • Ultimate Sound FX Bundle | Sidearm Studios

(All Assets are purchased through the Unity Asset Store)
